AMY WINEHOUSE 
The life-size bronze statue to the late AMY WINEHOUSE Winehouse was unveiled in Camden , London, on September 14 2014, on what would have been the singer's 31st birthday. There were some crtics of its accuracy but fans seemed generally happy that it looked like her, trademark beehive hairdo and all, and designer Scott Eaton said: "The design is not based on any single snapshot, photo or moment in time, but an amalgamation of influences." Picture: Getty Images
